data.description: Wonderful 3 bedroom 2 bath house in a quiet cul-de-sac in Harvey Crossing.  This home features a large fenced back yard, covered patio and a covered party deck. Inside you will find a large open plan with a fireplace, a nice spacious kitchen with a bar and an office with a desk and built-ins. This has become a must in todays work environment. The master bedroom has a double vanity, a jetted tub with separate shower and a large walk-in closet with built-ins.  Schedule your private showing soon before this one is gone!
